  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>每日发现最新LLM</span> <span>2026-03-06 18:40</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">中国香港</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=059baf39&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUibyxhuYSuFZLiaN5xUGF51mCFuhMk6jb1JEGmE4wEIwGM5EkYUjeUnnsZjgzgdbhS2jHahF4M2j8JEZgpbsWcQabQjIVk3p8QRDicFITRE70Q%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>Transformer注意力机制底层高性能优化算子FlashAttention-4，专注于隐私和安全的开源人工智能助手IronClaw，实时多视图扩散模型WorldFM，统一多样灵巧手的标准手部表示OHRA，可控的多镜头叙事视频生成框架MultiShotMaster，自动生成引擎优化框架AutoGEO</p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: center;line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 []\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100010333\" data-ratio=\"0.0859375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 389px;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=17b00053&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwuWicsSRFbFewfePZ1EiaVdtFvrJflfNa3P11kpGn8dhrOaAmmKQ3INqCXFZr2IrrUmmtkia9otecsw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 0px;text-align: left;\"><mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe mp_common_widget\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"机器之心SOTA模型\" data-alias=\"sotaai\" data-from=\"2\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/GU2ibjU7TDkyqTqr59u8fKegUibXxHSW3WF3ib6u8lQO8JicgNbPzicmhb8kPjrkYk6libDSD7ia1RlxQN9bWugwjguOg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"追踪 AI 开源进展，探索先进开发实践。\" data-id=\"MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：FlashAttention-4</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"647\" data-imgfileid=\"100018085\" data-ratio=\"0.4046296296296296\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b8fbd43c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFYz17x4r0Mt90JDxAz16kCUcqM4Rnyp5o0MicgoQicSLTtXpo74KoEBmXcr1yeuibc3Gic1rovbnjkKCY5OcEd9aLMx5S84J5t35c8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★FlashAttention-4是深度学习领域里程碑式的Transformer注意力机制底层高性能优化算子。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目针对NVIDIA Blackwell（B200/GB200）GPU全新重构算法流水线，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">突破硬件非对称扩展带来的SFU算力瓶颈与共享内存带宽限制</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，让注意力计算速度达到矩阵乘法级，集成了多项式指数模拟、条件式softmax重缩放、2CTA MMA指令、张量内存（TMEM）复用等核心优化，同时采用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">CuTe-DSL</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">编写实现极速编译。项目已正式开源，原生适配PyTorch FlexAttention，提供完整算子实现、技术论文与全流程GPU部署支持。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/flash-attention\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/flash-attention</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：IronClaw</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"839\" data-imgfileid=\"100018086\" data-ratio=\"0.524074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=879f0a17&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFYCgUlKWLbvJYDicQg28veYeaqiaXwJRx9RCHfdpfqWxDH7sNMOqvO57N06Y6XIHhfciaCzicA9bfdCySXrGzFdoM6LBdAMqaP5qyw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★IronClaw是一个专注于隐私和安全的开源人工智能助手，灵感来源于OpenClaw。它的设计原则是确保用户的数据始终由用户掌控，所有信息都在本地存储并加密，绝不离开用户的控制。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">IronClaw提供</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">透明</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的操作方式，没有隐藏的遥测或数据收集功能。用户可以</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">动态构建新工具</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，并通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">多层安全防护</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">来保护数据免受注入攻击和泄露。IronClaw支持多种渠道，包括REPL、HTTP webhooks、WASM通道（如Telegram、Slack）和Web网关，确保随时可用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ironclaw\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ironclaw</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：WorldFM</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"908\" data-imgfileid=\"100018089\" data-ratio=\"0.5675925925925925\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f864ed87&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFbWm9E83JJWuOd9behRYWsOsaZjOJTBiaBiauqYY3a87yONTcDOsInOPFXCPSia0haW7S1HCjopHOciahEcRra3QriajtSPYGUBFEbI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★WorldFM是一个实时多视图扩散模型。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">给定参考图像和目标相机姿态，WorldFM可以在这些新视点生成图像。该项目支持用户通过替换开源全景生成模型来实现一致的场景生成，而不影响核心的空间推理框架。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/worldfm\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/worldfm</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：OHRA</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"617\" data-imgfileid=\"100018087\" data-ratio=\"0.3851851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5d406def&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFYOq91PWnLuBMW0vX6B3noMOqNoxr7M4lg9n6q3q5ceDZ5AJxJ390RRCibLmAZ46bliaPdd1XZl8icmQXSumuqCPU6IibtA7rQiasvE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★OHRA项目提出了一种统一多样灵巧手的标准手部表示，将其整合到一个共享的参数空间和标准的URDF格式中。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">这种表示方法为</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">跨形态策略学习</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">提供了条件，能够实现灵巧抓取和对新手形态的零样本泛化，展示了其在广泛的灵巧操作任务中的潜力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ohra\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ohra</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：MultiShotMaster</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"653\" data-imgfileid=\"100018088\" data-ratio=\"0.4083333333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b5bc7d8c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFakvpV5Eq1hlaStoNQAiaultQuGLu5VaD9DbIIvIHds8ytqMzH9Z4WeWicU1eTTakKvNCuBWj3NFFbGFPATrVEEiaCapOjOsqMdLw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★MultiShotMaster是一个可控的多镜头叙事视频生成框架。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目支持文本驱动的镜头间一致性、可变的镜头数量和时长、定制化的主体运动控制以及背景驱动的场景定制。项目的开源版本基于Wan2.1-T2V-1.3B和Wan2.1-T2V-14B模型，提供了训练和推理代码以及模型检查点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/multishotmaster\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/multishotmaster</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：AutoGEO</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"502\" data-imgfileid=\"100018090\" data-ratio=\"0.3138888888888889\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=384cefd0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFaGjUwfZ8HHrI9eaLlR4ibDoUlpWMnzqJicGkyGgziamylwdyAgHjMFbBsPs9ia26mCya7Mia3NFEFrP17uwfhBLpLKCDFN8bPduh4I%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★AutoGEO是一个自动生成引擎优化（GEO）框架，旨在帮助网页内容在大语言模型生成的答案中获得更高的可见性。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目通过自动提取生成引擎的内容偏好规则，并重写文档以在不损害生成引擎效用的情况下最大化可见性。AutoGEO包含三个核心组件：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">规则提取</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">、</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">基于提示的GEO模型（AutoGEOAPI）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">通过强化学习训练的经济型GEO模型（AutoGEOMini）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/autogeo\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/autogeo</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: center;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"908\" data-imgfileid=\"100012181\" data-ratio=\"1.5712962962962962\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 578px;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=050dd75e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzsuveu0Oib7RPoas9iaReIDLd72zAJkrNOCp7A0IRgbeicADqBSicz36BLdGh2dz1C7E5PZgibCqFNSRQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"107\" data-imgfileid=\"100013546\" data-ratio=\"0.18518518518518517\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);letter-spacing: 0.578px;width: 578px;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=73250edd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDky46ibiaDkwPpOl085OGW8JMM572LKqicN8ordMGb1lKKwclv8NbFEOlFRqAojINufXDNiaERbIkUv8EQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe mp_common_widget\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"机器之心SOTA模型\" data-alias=\"sotaai\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/GU2ibjU7TDkyqTqr59u8fKegUibXxHSW3WF3ib6u8lQO8JicgNbPzicmhb8kPjrkYk6libDSD7ia1RlxQN9bWugwjguOg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"追踪 AI 开源进展，探索先进开发实践。\" data-id=\"MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==\"></mp-common-profile></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n  <p><a href=\"%27%27\">阅读原文</a></p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/link-proxy/?k=eca4d12b&amp;r=1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzkyMzcwMDIyMQ%3D%3D%26mid%3D2247501741%26idx%3D1%26sn%3D25ff7dbf1932060c53ada30d36db3bd1\">跳转微信打开</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文汇总了 2026 年 3 月初的六项前沿开源 AI 项目，重点介绍了针对 NVIDIA Blackwell 架构深度优化的 FlashAttention-4 及其底层性能突破。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文汇总了 2026 年 3 月初的六项前沿开源 AI 项目，重点介绍了针对 NVIDIA Blackwell 架构深度优化的 FlashAttention-4 及其底层性能突破。",
  "summary": "文章精选并简要介绍了六个最新的开源 AI 项目，涵盖了底层算子、隐私助手、多视图生成、机器人控制及搜索优化等多个维度。核心亮点是 FlashAttention-4，该项目针对 Blackwell GPU 进行了算法流水线重构，利用 2CTA MMA 指令和条件式 softmax 等技术，使注意力计算速度接近硬件极限。此外，文章还介绍了主打本地加密的 AI 助手 IronClaw、实时多视图扩散模型 WorldFM、统一灵巧手表示框架 OHRA、可控叙事视频生成框架 MultiShotMaster，以及针对 AI 搜索时代的生成引擎优化框架 AutoGEO。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "FlashAttention-4 实现了针对新一代硬件的底层算子极致优化。",
      "explanation": "通过重构算法流水线并引入 2CTA MMA 指令与张量内存复用，解决了 Blackwell 硬件的 SFU 算力瓶颈，使注意力计算达到矩阵乘法级速度。"
    },
    {
      "point": "隐私安全成为开源 AI 助手设计的核心原则。",
      "explanation": "IronClaw 项目强调数据主权，通过本地存储、全流程加密和无遥测设计，为用户提供了一个安全且透明的 AI 交互环境。"
    },
    {
      "point": "生成式 AI 正在向高可控性和跨形态泛化方向发展。",
      "explanation": "MultiShotMaster 提升了视频生成的镜头一致性，而 OHRA 则通过统一手部表示，实现了灵巧操作策略在不同机器人形态间的零样本泛化。"
    },
    {
      "point": "生成引擎优化（GEO）成为 AI 搜索时代的新兴技术方向。",
      "explanation": "AutoGEO 框架通过自动提取 LLM 的内容偏好并重写文档，旨在提升网页内容在 AI 生成答案中的可见性，类似于 AI 时代的 SEO。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "FlashAttention-4 让注意力计算速度达到矩阵乘法级，集成了多项式指数模拟、条件式 softmax 重缩放等核心优化。",
    "IronClaw 的设计原则是确保用户的数据始终由用户掌控，所有信息都在本地存储并加密，绝不离开用户的控制。",
    "AutoGEO 旨在帮助网页内容在大语言模型生成的答案中获得更高的可见性。",
    "OHRA 能够实现灵巧抓取和对新手形态的零样本泛化，展示了其在广泛的灵巧操作任务中的潜力。"
  ],
